Save your questions for break time. Let's continue
with the morning assembly.
Please take your seats, both of you.
(Is it time for elective classes now?)

(What should I do next? If I do the same as
before, the outcome won't change)

(I have to find the culprit and stop them before
then. Let's do our best)

Let's take action from the 21st to the 25th,
protecting Amelia while preventing the mysterious
ritual. We can attend classes during the day and
explore with Amelia after school.

You can also advance time without doing anything
by using the book on your desk in the classroom.

I have now become able to receive ritual magic
lessons in the new Ritual Magic Laboratory!
